	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Clerk&#39;s Office U S. Cir Court</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>St Paul</placeName> <date>Oct 30. 1862</date>.</p>
				<p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">At a meeting of the<lb/> Israelites of this city &#40;few in number&#41; freed<lb/> last <date>Sunday</date>&#44; it was proposed and<lb/> agreed to open a Jewish Sunday School<lb/> in this City under the instruction of a<lb/> <persName>Mr <hi rend="underline">Marcuson</hi></persName>&#44; with whom I believe you<lb/> are acquainted&#33;  And other movements<lb/> made for the purpose of Organizing a<lb/> Congregation here&#44; and for that purpose<lb/> the same gentleman was elected <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> <add>Hebrew</add>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I have been requested to order from you</p>
				<p>six copies of the large catechism for children</p>
				<p>&#8220;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; &#8220; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;small&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;  &#8220; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; &#8220; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; &#8220;</p>
				<p>12&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; &#8220; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;  &#8220; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Primer&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;  &#8220; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; &#8220;</p>
				<p>Will you have the kindness to forward them<lb/> by Express to me with your bill for the same<lb/> which will be immediately paid.</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Very truly yours</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)"><persName role="author">J N Cardoza</persName></p>
			
